    {
      "id": "3",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "Looks like you were zoning out for a second there.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_3",
      "next": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "Luck doesn't seem to be on your side today, does it?",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_4",
      "next": "5",

			"command": [
				"gambleth show_fake_chip_toast @p"
			]
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "You've lost all of your chips again...",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_5",
      "next": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "Well, you finally get a second chance today.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_6",
      "next": "7"
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "Our basement has recently been overrun with pests, and our janitor is not doing a very good job at getting rid of them.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_7",
      "next": "8"
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "(...to be frank, the amount he's getting paid might have to do something with it)",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_8",
      "next": "9"
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "I'll let you help him in exchange for some extra chips. Beware though, it's kinda dangerous out there.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_9",
      "next": "10"
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "He's waiting for you in the basement, go talk to him, he'll guide you to the place.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_10",
      "next": "11"
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "Oh, and make sure not to call him a janitor when he's around. He likes to refer to himself as a wizard, apparently.",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_11",
      "next": "12"
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "speaker": "Casino Master",
      "portraits": [
        {
          "path": "gcat.png",
          "position": "INLINE"
        } 
      ],
      "text": "(god, this guy)",
      "audio": "entity.gcat_welcome_12"
    }
  ]
